productReviews.reviewText: My neighbor Fannie has one of these. She works as a teacher and she says it looks spiky.
My co-worker Kazuo has one of these. He says it looks transparent.
SoCal cockroaches are unwelcome, crafty, and tenacious. This groupware keeps them away.
